 <h3>Exponentiation and the remainder operators must be without a unit. Therefore we need to define an unitless scalar</h3>
 <p>
  <span class="eq">
   <b>
    <var>m1</var>
   </b>
   =
   <span class="matrix">
    <span class="tr">
     <span class="td">
     </span>
     <span class="td">
      10
      <i>°C</i>
     </span>
     <span class="td">
     </span>
    </span>
    <span class="tr">
     <span class="td">
     </span>
     <span class="td">
      -5.5
      <i>°C</i>
     </span>
     <span class="td">
     </span>
    </span>
    <span class="tr">
     <span class="td">
     </span>
     <span class="td">
      3.14
      <i>°C</i>
     </span>
     <span class="td">
     </span>
    </span>
    <span class="tr">
     <span class="td">
     </span>
     <span class="td">
      -7
      <i>°C</i>
     </span>
     <span class="td">
     </span>
    </span>
    <span class="tr">
     <span class="td">
     </span>
     <span class="td">
      8.88
      <i>°C</i>
     </span>
     <span class="td">
     </span>
    </span>
   </span>
  </span>
 </p>
 <p>
 </p>
 <p>
  <span class="eq">
   <var>scalar</var>
   <sub>unitless</sub>
   = -4.7
  </span>
 </p>
 <p>
 </p>
 <p>
  <span class="eq">
   <b>
    <var>c</var>
   </b>
   =
   <b>
    <var>m1</var>
   </b>
   <sup>
    <small class="nth">⊙</small>
    <var>scalar</var>
    <sub>unitless</sub>
   </sup>
   =
   <b>
    <var>m1</var>
   </b>
   <sup>
    <small class="nth">⊙</small>
    -4.7
   </sup>
   =
   <span class="matrix">
    <span class="tr">
     <span class="td">
     </span>
     <span class="td">
      2×10
      <sup>-5</sup>
      <i>°C</i>
      <sup class="unit">-4.7</sup>
     </span>
     <span class="td">
     </span>
    </span>
    <span class="tr">
     <span class="td">
     </span>
     <span class="td">
      <span class="err">Undefined</span>
      <i>°C</i>
      <sup class="unit">-4.7</sup>
     </span>
     <span class="td">
     </span>
    </span>
    <span class="tr">
     <span class="td">
     </span>
     <span class="td">
      0.00462
      <i>°C</i>
      <sup class="unit">-4.7</sup>
     </span>
     <span class="td">
     </span>
    </span>
    <span class="tr">
     <span class="td">
     </span>
     <span class="td">
      <span class="err">Undefined</span>
      <i>°C</i>
      <sup class="unit">-4.7</sup>
     </span>
     <span class="td">
     </span>
    </span>
    <span class="tr">
     <span class="td">
     </span>
     <span class="td">
      3.49×10
      <sup>-5</sup>
      <i>°C</i>
      <sup class="unit">-4.7</sup>
     </span>
     <span class="td">
     </span>
    </span>
   </span>
  </span>
 </p>
 <p>
  <span class="eq">
   <var>f</var>
   (
   <var>m1</var>
   ;
   <var>scalar</var>
   <sub>unitless</sub>
   )  =
   <var>m1</var>
   <sup>
    <var>scalar</var>
